{"tid":1666781,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(開始滅口) 水警警長倒斃私家車內 警封鎖現場調查","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T19:19:54.000Z","uid":222970,"like":429,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"1c2e5fcd4add48362999e88e95d4b8c01c3c10f8","tid":1666781,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"(開始滅口) 水警警長倒斃私家車內 警封鎖現場調查<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-21 13:22<br />\n<br />\n落馬洲石湖圍路一處山路，警方於早上9時16分接獲市民報案，指發現一名男子倒臥在一輛私家車內無反應。警方及救援人員到場，經檢驗證實事主已經死亡。警方暫列屍體發現案處理，現正封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n據現場消息稱，死者年約40歲，是一名水警警長，隷屬水警北分區。前日(19日)疑與妻子因事曾起爭執，事主事後駕車離家。其妻昨日(20日)前往落馬洲警署報案。人員隨即四處尋找，惟今晨揭發悲劇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y6ASrbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy6ASrbL.jpg&h=029aa1b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfe30063b7ca6f20701de4f5802ebd793a798589","tid":1666781,"uid":47605,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c71b9ef8728bffac86c932920111ce436f657c","tid":1666781,"uid":222970,"like":121,"dislike":0,"score":121,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"To mon post狗 中共依家滅口啦 你地連造園都冇得入啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3514b5c27e7deece390973f9c42a419643afe6bf","tid":1666781,"uid":92385,"like":155,"dislike":1,"score":154,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:30:50.000Z","msg":"水警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浮屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陳彥霖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2477ffdb4578c76f4dec1eef582e8c592dfd7fc4","tid":1666781,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re